>"},{"pid":"313d105ad8a912374f42b1cf698c99e2ab3828e9","tid":1313774,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:24:48.000Z","msg":"槍響之前：金恩博士與三個邪惡的最後鬥爭<br />\n人們當然知道馬丁路德金恩博士為黑人民權運動奮鬥，知道他著名的演說「我有一個夢」，或者知道他在整整五十年前的1968年被槍殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40soundfury%2F%25E6%25A7%258D%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D-%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%2582%25AA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD-c3dd35a3dcf4&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=8aac7927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4</a><br />\n泛民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.不受傷，不流血。<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ee164015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a>"},{"pid":"6968c74f4ecdec5de7178c27f75def95f25a1479","tid":1313774,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化</code></pre>"},{"pid":"01fb0